FriendlyNamePlural="Reinforced Shield Frames"
BriefSummary="A modification of our Plated SPARK Armor, this variation sacrifices mobility for improved durability. It features heavier plating and additional reactive armor to negate incoming damage."
TacticalText="<Bullet/> Provides increased armor and hit points, at the expense of mobility and defense. Also reduces wound recovery times by 2 HP."

[PlatedSparkLightArmor_LW X2SparkArmorTemplate_DLC_3]
