FriendlyNamePlural="Reinforced Mobility Frames"
BriefSummary="A modification of our Plated SPARK Armor, this variation sacrifices durability for improved mobility and additional arm control capacitors. It grants the Dedication ability and allows the SPARK to use its Kinetic Strike more often."
